snippet.title: Cat Warfare Trailer
snippet.description:
Cat Warfare Trailer

Subscribe for more content!

Cat Warfare is a multiplayer first person shooter that lets you take the place of a cat out for revenge, blood and glory.

Buy the game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/923370/Cat_Warfare/
Join our discord: https://discord.gg/TmrMx8P
Twitter: https://twitter.com/NSClassicGames

If you found this video enjoyable, give it a like.
If you would like to show someone, share it.
Leave a comment below with your thoughts.

Good luck and its going to be one heck of a cat fight.
Don't forget to subscribe!

#CatWarfare
